Thomas D. ARTHUR, petitioner,
v.
Jefferson S. DUNN, Commissioner, Alabama Department of Corrections, et al.
No. 16-1408 (16A1161).
Supreme Court of the United States
May 25, 2017.
Application for stay of execution of sentence of death presented to Justice THOMAS and by him refereed to the Court denied. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Eleventh Circuit denied.
